      "raw": "# But the tr(6E + R Id)/6 = tr(6*(R/4)*Id + R*Id)/6 = tr((3R/2 + R)*Id)/6",
      "type": "comment",
      "context": "a_2 = (4pi)^{-4} tr(R/6 Id + E) Vol = (4pi)^{-4} * 16 * (R/6 + R/4) Vol = (4pi)^{-4} * 16 * (5R/12) Vol",
